sops.sop:
Workflow:
1. User -> Transportation Planner;
2. Transportation Planner -> Accommodation Planner 
   Transportation Planner -> Restaurant Planner 
   Transportation -> Attractions Planner (in parallel);
3. Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, Attractions Planner -> Plan Checker;
4. Plan Checker -> Final Plan Summarizer;
5. Final Plan Summarizer -> End.

Description:
First, the Transportation Planner determines inter-city transportation and daily locations. This framework is shared with Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, and Attractions Planner, who work in parallel to find optimal options. The Plan Checker reviews for inconsistencies and budget compliance, then the Final Plan Summarizer compiles the verified data into a detailed itinerary.
